'''Burgersdorp''' i muti lowu kumekaka e ka [[masipala wa xifundza xa Mopani]] e xifundzeni-nkulu xa [[Limpopo]] e [[Afrika Dzonga]]. Muti lowu wule kule hi 32 wa tikhilomitara kusuka e dzongeni bya vuxa bya doroba ra [[Tzaneen]] e patwini ra  R36 ro ya e [[Phalaborwa]].<ref name="census2011">{{cite web |url=http://census2011.adrianfrith.com/place/962081 |title = Main Place Burgersdorp |work=Census 2011}} </ref>

